  "time_ut": 1657114136,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dab \u0d85\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0d87\u0dad\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0daf\u0dc5 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The elephant's tusks were cut off with an axe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Chandana Jayasinghe, Anuradhapura Wildlife Veterinary Officer, said that one of the elephant's tusks was cut off with the help of an ax by someone who was seriously injured in a duel with an elephant.",
        "Kabithigollewa Thittagonewa Moraoya had a tooth of a saddhanta cut off in this way.",
        "After a fight with another elephant in a forest near Kabithigollewa Nabadawewa, this elephant got seriously injured and came to the edge of Eripiniwewa water and the wildlife officers started treating this elephant.",
        "Dr. Chandana Jayasinghe says that the officials treated the elephant continuously for almost three weeks."
      ],
